{"tid":725252,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[dse有意入中大入一入黎] 高質cheer, 高質餐廳, 高質打手, 高質dse分數 盡在中大","createTime":"2018-07-01T15:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T07:15:56.000Z","uid":103616,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"918a6f90024a6ee0276dd22bb955e1b8620a3f0d","tid":725252,"uid":103616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:18:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">高質cheer</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NLlJqKxJnWA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNLlJqKxJnWA&d=EgHo0OhfCLsmNdJjH%2FLCPzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=efbfc569\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NLlJqKxJnWA</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.southcn.com/gate/big5/news.southcn.com/hktwma/hot/200208291051.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.southcn.com%2Fgate%2Fbig5%2Fnews.southcn.com%2Fhktwma%2Fhot%2F200208291051.htm&d=EgHo0OhfCLsmNdJjH%2FLCPzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=25cbea4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://big5.southcn.com/gate/big5/news.southcn.com/hktwma/hot/200208291051.htm</a><br />\n為咗提供良好性教育同教授良好舒壓方法，中大為各位新生設立不同種類cheer口號<br />\n內容有北上dup骨，召妓，SM等<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「鍾意北上去dup骨 搞到全身生粒粒」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「無波仲着小背心」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「汁多肉厚好騎呢」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「XX女仔扮密實，西門大開任進入」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「崇基女宿係妓寨，鍾意SM好變態」<br />\n「組仔叫雞唔俾錢，組女做雞好淫賤」<br />\n「聯合組媽最盡責﹐含吹舐啜有方法﹐皆因家法好嚴格」<br />\n「崇基啲女好淫賤，晚晚都要玩坐蓮，重要棍上舞翩翩，苦練冰火五重天」<br />\n「崇基啲仔係舞男，被女搞到生晒癌，個個切晒做太監，入宮等新亞嚟探」<br />\n「逸夫起頭真係難，冇錢冇面人又煩，駐紮邊疆似嚿飯，調理農務杏加橙」</span></span></strong><br />\n為咗令到各位新生投入大學生活 組爸組媽會渾身解數逼大家大嗌以上口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">高質餐廳</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9aB3AFAqlso\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9aB3AFAqlso&d=EgHo0OhfCLsmNdJjH%2FLCPzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=553edd87\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9aB3AFAqlso</a><br />\n中大飯廳已經預備各類昆蟲，令到新生適應細菌病毒，提升免疫力<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">高質打手</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/702197/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/702197/page/2</a><br />\n於lihkg，以CUHKBanters為首的高質會員為咗突顯中大嘅幽默感：以收入為標準，證明中大排名高過科大，點知原來用呢個標準垃圾學店排名原來高過中大<br />\n為咗證明中大排名高過港大，佢舉咗呢個研究做例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/172352_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F172352_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=46b56f5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點知研究第一名竟然係科大<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">高質dse分數</span></strong><br />\n一向出名<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三大名氣 嶺大分數</span></span>嘅中大工程，最新年度LQ係20分<br />\n如果想一入到黎就屌打全部人，中大工程會係你必然選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中大歡迎你 記住A1 A2 A3都要擺中大</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b09d99c94a2373418864a52b0e94710dc21a878","tid":725252,"uid":132968,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"你鐘意啦, 反正想入中大個批大部份都唔上 LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你睇中大個討論 post 一個 sem 先一次 1001<br />\n<br />\n點似得科大嗰一個, 唔使幾日就要開新嘅post<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連登大多數毒撚, 毒撚大多數入科大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19731edca8dcdf7b69161405460880514634c2ad","tid":725252,"uid":103616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b09d99c94a2373418864a52b0e94710dc21a878","tid":725252,"uid":132968,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"你鐘意啦, 反正想入中大個批大部份都唔上 LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你睇中大個討論 post 一個 sem 先一次 1001<br />\n<br />\n點似得科大嗰一個, 唔使幾日就要開新嘅post<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連登大多數毒撚, 毒撚大多數入科大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:32:16.000Z","msg":"你咪就係中大剩低啲小部分毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nps 唔係科大"},{"pid":"9eb9e53be2f24dc30ac42084f0a41f05d3ba3fb6","tid":725252,"uid":132968,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:34:17.000Z","msg":"btw UST QSA 2017 DSE Lowest: 18<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n恆管分數, 亞洲 MIT 名氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n科大幫到你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc626fc31e25b8fb4b28e3b26bad29560b3f3e29","tid":725252,"uid":103616,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"9b09d99c94a2373418864a52b0e94710dc21a878","tid":725252,"uid":132968,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"你鐘意啦, 反正想入中大個批大部份都唔上 LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你睇中大個討論 post 一個 sem 先一次 1001<br />\n<br />\n點似得科大嗰一個, 唔使幾日就要開新嘅post<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連登大多數毒撚, 毒撚大多數入科大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:34:26.000Z","msg":"CUHKBanters一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看著他笑。<br />\n<br />\n有的叫道，「CUHKBanters，你怎麼又回來校園台了！」<br />\n<br />\n他不回答，對櫃裡說，「溫兩碗酒，要一本教科書。」便排出九文大錢。<br />\n<br />\n他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又厚著臉皮回來了！」<br />\n<br />\nCUHKBanters睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你被眾巴打恥笑，吊著打。」<br />\n<br />\nCUHKBanters便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「隱退不能算趕&hellip;&hellip;隱退！&hellip;&hellip;IQ135的ib English HL7/7，還會被趕麼？」<br />\n<br />\n接連便是難懂的話，什麼「Tell that to your HR」，什麼「still living in your own imaginary world」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"58c5c134e2b6c1e26aaaa0e77f21ac506a296b51","tid":725252,"uid":103616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9eb9e53be2f24dc30ac42084f0a41f05d3ba3fb6","tid":725252,"uid":132968,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:34:17.000Z","msg":"btw UST QSA 2017 DSE Lowest: 18<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n恆管分數, 亞洲 MIT 名氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n科大幫到你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/172352_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F172352_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=46b56f5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人地科大勁過你垃圾中大wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cbec0a21f41a889c70f77e80c7a3a4fa585108","tid":725252,"uid":132968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":